# 🧠 Mini PC Server / NAS (Planned)

## 📌 Status
Planned

---

## 🎯 Objective

Introduce a dedicated low-power Mini PC to handle all server and storage workloads.

---

## 🧠 Why This Change?

- Separate server from user systems
- Improve reliability and uptime
- Reduce power consumption
- Create a true homelab architecture

---

## ⚙️ Planned Roles

- NAS (file storage)
- Docker host
- Media server (Jellyfin)
- Game servers (e.g., Minecraft)
- Development environment

---

## 🔄 Migration Plan

- Move services from current secondary PC
- Reconfigure network services
- Optimize storage layout

---

## 📈 Expected Benefits

- Always-on system
- Lower power usage
- Better performance isolation
- Cleaner infrastructure design
